value.0: Welcome to the Providence Temple.  How can I help you?
I cannot, but you can use the chat command <StartAction>!delete</Start> to do so.  Simply use the command, target yourself, then confirm the deletion.
How many levels would you like to relevel?
If you have Legendary Levels, Pale Master, or RDD levels you are unable to relevel.  You must delete your character and use the xp bank.  The chat commands are !delete and !xpbank.
What would you like your alignment to be changed too?
Are you sure?  All items in your loot bag(s) that can be sold, will be.
I've made a mistake with my character, can you help me?
I would like to be releveled.
